title: DFIP-03: CFMC #2 DUNG VOTING
body:
Howdy farmers!

It's time to select the winner of the second Country Folks Meme Contest! The  theme of this contest is 'Metaverse Farming' and we've got a lot of great entries. Huge thanks to each and every participant! 

Here’s the list of candidates in no particular order:

Next CFMC #3 is coming shortly, don’t miss it!
